<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Internship Application Viewed</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #222; }
      .container { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; }
      .title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
      .muted { color: #666; }
      .footer { margin-top: 24px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="title">We've viewed your internship application</div>
      <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
      <p>Thanks for applying for the <strong><%= internshipField %></strong> internship at our lab. We wanted to let you know that your application has been viewed. Once it is fully reviewed, we'll get back to you soon.</p>
      <p class="muted">No action is required from your side at the moment.</p>
      <div class="footer">This is an automated message. Please do not reply.</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
